Date><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldiers-at-sensitive-security-sites-reveal-their-identity-and-location-online/00000191-326a-d9ba-a5df-7a7b855a0000</guid></item><item><title>尽管一再下令以色列警方不要没收反战抗议标语</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-continue-confiscating-anti-war-protest-signs-despite-repeated-orders-not-to/00000191-3249-dedb-abb7-7769e0ee0000</link><description>国家检察官办公室表示，禁止扣押政治标牌的命令已广泛传阅六次，但均被忽视</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 14:50:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-continue-confiscating-anti-war-protest-signs-despite-repeated-orders-not-to/00000191-3249-dedb-abb7-7769e0ee0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡告诉《时代》杂志，他对 10 月 7 日事件感到“抱歉”，现在“不是提出问责问题的时候”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/netanyahu-tells-time-hes-sorry-for-oct-7-now-not-the-time-to-accept-accountability/00000191-3238-d2d3-af9d-3ebda9430000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡表示，加沙战争结束后，将成立一个“独立委员会，对10月7日之前发生的一切进行审查”，并且“每个人都必须回答一些棘手的问题，包括我”</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 14:43:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/netanyahu-tells-time-hes-sorry-for-oct-7-now-not-the-time-to-accept-accountability/00000191-3238-d2d3-af9d-3ebda9430000</guid></item><item><title>以色列准备应对极右翼部长关于饿死加沙人的言论的后果</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-braces-for-fallout-of-far-right-ministers-comments-on-starving-gazans-to-death/00000191-31dc-d7be-a395-33fe6eb70001</link><description>欧盟国家、英国和其他国家谴责右翼部长的“令人震惊和有害的言论”，他表示国际压力是以色列没有饿死加沙人的唯一原因</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 14:16:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-braces-for-fallout-of-far-right-ministers-comments-on-starving-gazans-to-death/00000191-31dc-d7be-a395-33fe6eb70001</guid></item><item><title>维基百科编辑总结：以色列正在加沙实施种族灭绝</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/english-wikipedia-editors-concluded-israel-is-committing-genocide-in-gaza/00000191-321a-d4dc-a397-bf1e3fba0000</link><description>自从世界上最受欢迎的在线网站的编辑上个月投票决定将维基百科条目重命名为“加沙种族灭绝”并删除了之前的“指控”一词以来，该条目每天都有数以万计的浏览量</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 13:43:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/english-wikipedia-editors-concluded-israel-is-committing-genocide-in-gaza/00000191-321a-d4dc-a397-bf1e3fba0000</guid></item><item><title>选择辛瓦尔作为政治领袖巩固了战争而非外交作为哈马斯命运的关键</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/choosing-sinwar-as-political-chief-cements-war-not-diplomacy-as-key-to-hamas-fate/00000191-319c-dc5a-adf5-33be8fef0000</link><description>辛瓦尔被任命为哈马斯政治局局长应被视为一种意向宣言：哈马斯明白，加沙实地发生的事情比外交更能决定战争的结果，因此将权力移交给了当地政府。地面指挥部</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 12:14:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/choosing-sinwar-as-political-chief-cements-war-not-diplomacy-as-key-to-hamas-fate/00000191-319c-dc5a-adf5-33be8fef0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列撤销八名挪威外交官在巴勒斯坦权力机构的地位，作为承认巴勒斯坦的惩罚</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-revokes-eight-norwegian-diplomats-status-as-punishment-for-recognizing-palestine/00000191-317f-d4dc-a397-bd7f882d0000</link><description>以色列外交部宣布撤销八名挪威外交官的外交身份，这将有效阻止挪威在以色列和约旦河西岸的活动；挪威：“这是一种极端行为”</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 11:38:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-revokes-eight-norwegian-diplomats-status-as-punishment-for-recognizing-palestine/00000191-317f-d4dc-a397-bd7f882d0000</guid></item><item><title>血液、柴油和发电机：以色列的医疗系统如何为与真主党的战争做准备</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/blood-and-generators-how-israels-healthcare-system-is-preparing-for-war-with-hezbollah/00000191-3123-d1b4-a399-7da714850000</link><description>“我们现在不储存的东西在与真主党的战争期间不会存在”：以色列各地的医院正在通过储存医疗和手术用品、数千单位的血液以及柴油和汽油来为战争做准备</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 10:56:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/blood-and-generators-how-israels-healthcare-system-is-preparing-for-war-with-hezbollah/00000191-3123-d1b4-a399-7da714850000</guid></item><item><title>以色列做出具有里程碑意义的决定，授予乌干达犹太人公民身份</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-grants-citizenship-to-ugandan-jew-in-landmark-decision/00000191-2dd1-d1b4-a399-7df7ac820000</link><description>七年四次皈依：乌干达阿巴尤达亚社区成员约瑟夫·基比塔 (Yosef Kibita) 进行了一场漫长的法律斗争，以获得作为犹太人移民的资格</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 10:47:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-grants-citizenship-to-ugandan-jew-in-landmark-decision/00000191-2dd1-d1b4-a399-7df7ac820000</guid></item><item><title>高级官员表示，以色列警方不会调查极右翼暴徒袭击以色列国防军基地的事件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/police-arent-investigating-storming-of-idf-bases-by-far-right-mobs-senior-officer-says/00000191-3153-d4e2-a9dd-b37f214f0000</link><description>极右翼示威者闯入斯德泰曼和拜特利德的以色列军事基地，那里关押着涉嫌虐待巴勒斯坦被拘留者的以色列国防军士兵，一周半后，没有人受到讯问或逮捕——尽管冲突被媒体捕捉到。视频</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 10:22:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/police-arent-investigating-storming-of-idf-bases-by-far-right-mobs-senior-officer-says/00000191-3153-d4e2-a9dd-b37f214f0000</guid></item><item><title>“我和你一起去”：本格维尔的警察局长在泄露的录音中宣誓效忠极右翼部长</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/im-with-you-ben-gvir-police-chief-pick-vows-allegiance-to-minister-in-leaked-recording/00000191-30d6-d386-adff-7dde8bf50000</link><description>在《国土报》获得的录音中，伊塔马尔·本·格维尔挑选的警察局长表示，尽管遭到以色列警方和内塔尼亚胡办公室的正式反对，他仍将支持拆除德鲁兹人的房屋</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 09:32:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/im-with-you-ben-gvir-police-chief-pick-vows-allegiance-to-minister-in-leaked-recording/00000191-30d6-d386-adff-7dde8bf50000</guid></item><item><title>美国希望阻止伊朗对以色列的重大袭击，而真主党仍然是未知因素</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/fearing-catastrophic-war-biden-warns-iran-against-attack-pushes-pm-to-make-deal/00000191-2de7-da6f-af99-2de71f1d0000</link><description>美国和以色列官员相信，真主党对杀害一名高级官员的报复将集中在军事地点，但他们不能肯定地说，真主党会多么谨慎地避免伤害平民</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 03:00:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/fearing-catastrophic-war-biden-warns-iran-against-attack-pushes-pm-to-make-deal/00000191-2de7-da6f-af99-2de71f1d0000</guid></item><item><title>现在发号施令，辛瓦尔的收购不会改变以色列与哈马斯协议的条款</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/sinwars-promotion-likely-wont-change-in-hamas-stance-in-hostage-talks-with-israel/00000191-2e07-d1b4-a399-7ea78a9c0000</link><description>辛瓦尔作为哈马斯政治局局长的新角色，负责监督军事和政治部门，这并没有改变以色列与哈马斯协议的动态，目前正在等待内塔尼亚胡的回应。他的任命是为了确保哈马斯的政治和财政未来，这可能比军事挑战更重要</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 03:00:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/sinwars-promotion-likely-wont-change-in-hamas-stance-in-hostage-talks-with-israel/00000191-2e07-d1b4-a399-7ea78a9c0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡很想解雇他的国防部长，但不相信其他选择</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-would-love-to-boot-his-defense-minister-but-doesnt-trust-the-alternative/00000191-2e3c-da6f-af99-2e7e6c7d0000</link><description>由于大多数联盟认为全面的地区战争是一个有价值的目标，总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡似乎将坚持国防部长约阿夫·加兰特 — — 至少目前如此</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 03:00:14 GMT</pubDate><g