talks-still-stuck/00000191-2e0e-d4e9-a7b7-2fce7d1c0000</guid></item><item><title>在以色列最后的常态堡垒中，紧张地等待伊朗的报复</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-07/ty-article/.highlight/in-israels-last-bastions-of-normalcy-waiting-nervously-for-irans-revenge/00000191-2d53-d1b4-a399-7df7cc470000</link><description>这种等待的游戏是攻击的一部分——哈桑·纳斯鲁拉甚至说过同样的话——也许伊朗和真主党希望悬念确实会杀死我们</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 18:48:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-07/ty-article/.highlight/in-israels-last-bastions-of-normalcy-waiting-nervously-for-irans-revenge/00000191-2d53-d1b4-a399-7df7cc470000</guid></item></channel></rss>